News Center | 20.02.2024 | Each year, the Munich Security Summit, which was held by the imperialist states, especially capitalists and war barons, was protested in Munich on 17 February with the participation of thousands of opposition to war. Atik and YDG participated in the march by the Anti -Siko Platform with the banner “Let's stand against imperialist aggression together”.

The Zionist Israeli state's genocide in Palestine condemned the genocide of Palestine. In addition, imperialist countries, especially Germany, supported the attacks of the Zionist Israeli state. During the march, the Internationalist Solidarity was shouted with slogans.
